init_text: An alien has kidnapped Matt Damon, not knowing what lengths humanity goes through to retrieve him whenever he goes missing.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The President is personally involved, and the CIA, FBI, and NSA are all on the case.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is located in a remote area of the planet, and the President orders a strike force to be sent.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The strike force is comprised of a dozen of the most elite soldiers in the world, all with special abilities.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien is holding a hand-held device, and it speaks in a deep, raspy voice: "I have the human.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The lead soldier, a man with a dark complexion and a scar on his face, says, "We're gonna need a bigger gun."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien responds, "I'm not gonna hurt him.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The soldier says, "I'm gonna need your autograph, too."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The soldiers all fall to the ground, unconscious.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Matt signs, and the alien says, "Thanks, man.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The alien then teleports away, leaving Matt alone in the desert.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The soldiers all look at each other, and then they all start beating Matt with their weapons.
